sparql_query_kg2:
 Certainly! Given the provided information, here is the SPARQL query for Wikidata (KG2) to find the films starring Clint Eastwood that he directed himself:

```sparql
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE {
  ?uri wdt:P57 wd:Q43203 ;
        wdt:P161 wd:Q43203 .
}
```

This query selects distinct URIs (?uri) where the film has Clint Eastwood (wd:Q43203) as the director (P57) and also has him as the starring actor (P161).

